<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالرُّشْدُ هُنَا:</span> إِصْلَاحُ المَالِ،<span class="c5"> بِأَنْ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- يَبِيعَ وَيَشْتَرِيَ فَلَا يُغْبَنَ غَالِباً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا يَبْذُلَ مَالَهُ فِي حَرَامٍ، وَغَيْرِ فَائِدَةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَوَلِيُّهُمْ حَالَ الحَجْرِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> الأَبُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> ثُمَّ وَصِيُّهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> ثُمَّ الحَاكِمُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَلَا يَتَصَرَّفُ لَهُمْ إِلَّا بِالأَحَظِّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُقْبَلُ قَوْلُهُ بَعْدَ فَكِّ حَجْرٍ فِي:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- مَنْفَعَةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَضَرُورَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَتَلَفٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- لَا فِي دَفْعِ مَالٍ بَعْدَ رُشْدٍ، إِلَّا مِنْ مُتَبَرِّعٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَتَعَلَّقُ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span class="c5"> دَيْنُ مَأْذُونٍ لَهُ:</span> بِذِمَّةِ سَيِّدٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>- وَدَينُ غَيْرِهِ، وَأَرْشُ جِنَايَةِ قِنٍّ،<span class="c5"> وَقِيَمُ مُتْلَفَاتِهِ:</span> بِرَقَبَتِهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>